1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 20 =

20
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:36,180
As the sword was wielded,

21
00:01:36,820 --> 00:01:38,300
branches and leaves fell off?

22
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:42,020
I learned that

23
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:43,980
she used to study and practice skills

24
00:01:44,060 --> 00:01:45,540
with her brothers

25
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:49,060
and she’s an excellent swordsman and rider.

26
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:51,220
But I’ve never seen her skills myself.

27
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:53,860
Nor did I ever expect

28
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:56,100
that a well-mannered person

29
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,340
like Danshu

30
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,180
would wield weapons.

31
00:02:03,380 --> 00:02:04,340
Maoze

32
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:07,300
saw it, though,

33
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:09,140
and tried it himself.

34
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:14,780
Your Majesty, I have something urgent.

35
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,020
Your Majesty!

36
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:18,100
Your Majesty!

37
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:19,580
Your Majesty!

38
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:23,020
Your Majesty!

39
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:24,060
What happened?

40
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:26,620
Your Majesty!

41
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:28,620
This...

42
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:32,020
Help me, Your Majesty!

43
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,300
Calm down. You’re safe.

44
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,380
I’ll ask an Imperial Physician

45
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:40,780
to treat your wound,

46
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:42,420
or you’ll be disfigured

47
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:44,340
and won’t look good

48
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,460
when performing the Peony Picking Dance.

49
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,340
If I’m unable

50
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:50,380
to dance before you,

51
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:51,260
I’d rather

52
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,820
break my hands and feet.

53
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:55,740
If I’m thrown out of the palace

54
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:57,980
and married to some rich and powerful man

55
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,260
or demoted to be a slave,

56
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,300
I’d rather

57
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:02,140
disfigure my face

58
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,980
to keep everyone away from me.

59
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:20,780
The Book of Rites says,

60
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,020
“Food and love

61
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,500
are two biggest desires”.

62
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:28,020
Sages listed love

63
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:29,660
and food

64
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,180
as the most instinctive desires.

65
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:36,340
We eat food every day.

66
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,180
Once we mature,

67
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:39,860
if the desire for love

68
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:42,020
can’t be met for long,

69
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:44,220
it may flood out

70
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:45,700
without control,

71
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:48,180
leading people astray

72
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:48,940
in the end.

73
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:52,180
As sinful as it is,

74
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,540
it can be tolerated.

75
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:56,820
The punishment shouldn’t be too harsh.

76
00:03:57,500 --> 00:03:58,580
Deducting her salary for this month

77
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,220
and giving her heavy labor
for a few days every month

78
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,620
are enough.

79
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:03,860
Yes, Your Highness.

80
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:06,380
But...

81
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:08,340
His Majesty adores her.

82
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,220
That makes him

83
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:13,020
know her better than others.

84
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:15,540
Leave her to him then.

85
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:20,780
I know

86
00:04:21,460 --> 00:04:22,900
her unparalleled beauty

87
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:23,980
makes others jealous.

88
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:26,140
This poor girl is an orphan.

89
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,700
I raised her myself.

90
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:31,540
I know

91
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:33,820
she’s arrogant and unruly,

92
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,700
but she means no harm.

93
00:04:37,340 --> 00:04:38,940
I can vouch for her with my life

94
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:41,140
that she has nothing to do

95
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,100
with that kind of rubbish.

96
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,700
Xu Lantiao set her up.

97
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:47,060
She’s

98
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:49,300
too stubborn.

99
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:52,380
Ever since she met you last time,

100
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:54,180
she’s firmly believed

101
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:56,220
that Your Majesty was the one

102
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,060
who comforted her

103
00:04:58,740 --> 00:04:59,980
in her saddest moment

104
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:01,660
when her rabbit

105
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:03,300
was bitten to death by a mouse.

106
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:05,940
So she’s determined

107
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:08,380
to follow Your Majesty.

108
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:11,180
I knew she was wild.

109
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:13,740
It’s my fault

110
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,140
that I failed to discipline her,

111
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,180
so I made the decision

112
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,140
to marry her off.

113
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:27,540
I begged Deputy Officer Yang

114
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,220
to get her out of the palace soon

115
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,820
and he agreed.

116
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:33,540
She was supposed to leave

117
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:36,460
in a few days.

118
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:40,500
But during Officer Ren’s inspection,

119
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:43,500
that vicious Xu Lantiao...

120
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,340
Your Majesty.

121
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,900
Don’t marry me off!

122
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:07,420
Your Majesty,

123
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,460
please allow me

124
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:10,220
to be your maid.

125
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,180
I can do anything.

126
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:12,460
I’ll be as good as others.

127
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:34,340
I won’t marry you to others.

128
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:14,740
I’ve already promised Bihan,

129
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:17,140
so starting from today, she belongs here

130
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:17,980
and won’t go back with you.

131
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,860
As for her title or rank,

132
00:07:21,420 --> 00:07:22,820
I’ll discuss it with the Empress.

133
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,100
After all,

134
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,580
she’s in charge of the harem.

135
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:30,140
About these found during the inspection,

136
00:07:39,420 --> 00:07:40,820
you and Shouzhong

137
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:42,260
can decide yourselves.

138
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,140
Both of you

139
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:46,500
were trained by the Empress Dowager

140
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,820
and you’re experienced.

141
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,220
I trust you.

142
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:52,660
Even if there’s any disagreement...

143
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,540
I...

144
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:55,700
I have none.

145
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:56,740
I...

146
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,260
You’re capable

147
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,420
and thorough.

148
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,700
You can work out

149
00:08:03,660 --> 00:08:05,060
your differences.

150
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:06,780
All I want to say is

151
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,220
all the staff members,

152
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,660
maids, eunuchs,

153
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,860
guards, stewardesses,

154
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:14,660
as you know,

155
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:17,300
most of them were born poor.

156
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:19,460
Be patient with them.

157
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,380
If they make mistakes,

158
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:24,180
don’t be too harsh on them.

159
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,420
I was wrong.

160
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:28,620
Lesson learned, Your Majesty.

161
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:34,180
You broke in

162
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,620
out of concern for Bihan.

163
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:38,980
That’s admirable

164
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,460
but you still should be punished.

165
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,540
You knew you made a mistake

166
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:46,540
and had Deputy Officer Yang tie your hands.

167
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,340
I know.

168
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,060
I understand

169
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:57,460
I can’t continue to be an instructor.

170
00:08:58,820 --> 00:08:59,980
I’ll accept

171
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,100
whatever punishment

172
00:09:03,180 --> 00:09:04,780
awaiting me.

173
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,900
Bihan is an innocent

174
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,100
yet fierce girl.

175
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:20,860
If you treat her well,

176
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,780
she’ll trust and respect you.

177
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,020
She doesn’t know much about other things

178
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:26,860
and I don’t want her to know.

179
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,220
As for what punishment should be given

180
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,060
for your mistake,

181
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:37,940
I’m not familiar

182
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:39,060
with the rules of the harem,

183
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:42,340
so it’s up to the Empress.

184
00:09:50,650 --> 00:09:56,274
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

185
00:09:56,340 --> 00:09:57,060
Go to bed.

186
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:01,380
That’s it?

187
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:04,883
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

188
00:10:05,387 --> 00:10:10,629
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

189
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:11,540
Your Majesty,

190
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:15,820
I love you.

191
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:17,540
I love you with my heart and soul.

192
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:22,220
I want to be with you for the rest of my life

193
00:10:23,780 --> 00:10:25,860
and have lots of babies with you.

194
00:10:27,895 --> 00:10:31,510
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

195
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:34,140
I dared not keep those

196
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:37,380
who put me before the state.

197
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:39,380
Bihan,

198
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:41,940
you’re the only exception.

199
00:10:45,180 --> 00:10:46,100
Throughout my life,

200
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,940
other people and things

201
00:10:50,460 --> 00:10:51,540
belong to the Emperor.

202
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:56,260
Only you belong to me.

203
00:11:08,260 --> 00:11:12,620
= Yan Mansion =

204
00:11:23,940 --> 00:11:24,820
Father.

205
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:27,820
Father?

206
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:29,660
It’s late.

207
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:31,100
You should go back and rest.

208
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:32,540
You have morning court tomorrow.

209
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,260
Morning court?

210
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:36,700
Yes, morning court.

211
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:37,580
Let me help you.

212
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:40,980
Hypothetically,

213
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:44,180
if someone

214
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:46,580
separated you from your birth mother

215
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,980
when you were little,

216
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,100
gave you others’ children

217
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:53,420
to inherit your property

218
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:55,020
when you grew up,

219
00:11:55,660 --> 00:11:56,420
you would

220
00:11:56,980 --> 00:11:59,380
never want to see him again, wouldn’t you?

221
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:03,220
Father.

222
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:07,180
Careful.

223
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:20,300
Your Majesty,

224
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:22,620
Her Highness has arrived.

225
00:12:45,060 --> 00:12:46,340
My uncle

226
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:48,140
gave me his armor

227
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:49,860
when I was young.

228
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:54,220
It’s also my most valuable dowry.

229
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:06,020
Sadly, I’m a woman

230
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:07,940
and an empress,

231
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:11,340
I won’t be able

232
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:12,260
to fight on the battlefield in it.

233
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:15,940
So,

234
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:18,500
I’m giving it to you

235
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:20,940
so that one day,

236
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:23,420
a new general to pacify the west

237
00:13:23,420 --> 00:13:24,380
can wear it

238
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:28,220
to wipe out the barbarians for the locals.

239
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:44,220
Thank you, General Cao

240
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:52,380
and thank you as well.

241
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:55,540
I’ve decided

242
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:57,380
on the generals.

243
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,820
Although they’re inferior to General Cao,

244
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,860
I hope

245
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:07,100
once he sees this armor in heaven,

246
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:09,980
he can bless our army

247
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:11,860
to be as formidable

248
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:13,180
as that led by him.

249
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:21,060
I’ve decided to adopt Zongshi.

250
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:23,300
He’s likely

251
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:24,820
to become

252
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:26,180
my successor in the future.

253
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:28,620
I’ll entrust you

254
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:31,820
to raise the future heir.

255
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:53,740
Rise.

256
00:15:07,220 --> 00:15:11,180
= 1040 A.D. =

257
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:18,700
= Princess Huirou =
Bird.

258
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:21,900
Bird.

259
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:23,500
Bird.

260
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:24,580
Bird.

261
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:25,740
Where are you?

262
00:15:27,220 --> 00:15:28,100
Bird.

263
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:29,260
Where are you?

264
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:30,660
Miss Gao.

265
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:32,260
Princess.

266
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:34,620
Let’s go back to eat cheese.

267
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:35,980
I don’t want to.

268
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,860
I want the singing bird.

269
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:40,740
Your Highness,

270
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:42,140
Concubine Miao has arrived.

271
00:15:43,260 --> 00:15:44,140
Xinhe.

272
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,700
Come here and look.

273
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:49,580
Seedlings of the early maturing rice sprouted.

274
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:51,980
It was seven or eight days

275
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:53,140
earlier than last year.

276
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:54,820
In this case,

277
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:57,420
we can plant rice twice a year around the Capital,

278
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:59,820
and three times in regions south to Huai River.

279
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:03,660
I haven’t seen you so excited

280
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:05,100
for a while.

281
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:12,020
The war in the west won’t end soon.

282
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:14,260
What supports it

283
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:16,500
is mostly money and grains.

284
00:16:17,900 --> 00:16:19,660
Since Yuanhao rebelled last year,

285
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:21,940
markets at the border have been closed.

286
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,300
Although the Tanguts suffered a bigger loss,

287
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:26,340
people in our country

288
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:28,140
must be in panic

289
00:16:28,140 --> 00:16:29,460
even with enough supplies to use.

290
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:32,460
Hoarding continues

291
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,180
despite repeated prohibitions.

292
00:16:34,580 --> 00:16:35,660
Harsh laws and punishments

293
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:37,260
only increase the fear.

294
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:39,580
What can pacify them

295
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:41,420
is a good harvest

296
00:16:41,900 --> 00:16:43,100
of crops.

297
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:45,060
Over the past year,

298
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:47,580
His Majesty’s clothes have become loose.

299
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,740
Every time I comb his hair,

300
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:51,420
I’ll find

301
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:53,700
more gray hairs.

302
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,100
Sadly, I’m uneducated.

303
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:59,580
He couldn’t share

304
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,420
his problems with me.

305
00:17:03,100 --> 00:17:04,380
Huirou is

306
00:17:04,380 --> 00:17:05,740
his biggest source of joy.

307
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:07,540
Your Highness. Your Highness.

308
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:14,060
Your Highness,

309
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:15,340
= Gao Taotao =
Princess refuses to come back

310
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,060
and demands to find singing birds.

311
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:20,580
Birds?

312
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:23,380
Fan Yong’s report arrived from Yanzhou.

313
00:17:24,220 --> 00:17:26,700
He says Yuanhao failed to occupy Jinmingzhai
(today Ansai in Shaanxi)

314
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:27,620
after several attempts,

315
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,260
and proposed to make peace.

316
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:31,660
What do you think?

317
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:42,900
Be seated, Prime Minister Zhang.

318
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,300
Thank you, Your Majesty.

319
00:17:50,380 --> 00:17:51,220
In the past,

320
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:54,020
we were friendly to Tangut

321
00:17:54,660 --> 00:17:56,580
and few troops were stationed at the border.

322
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:59,300
That’s why they could raid us so many times

323
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:02,660
and Yuanhao’s rebelliousness grew.

324
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,580
Eventually, in 1038 A.D.,

325
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:07,300
he proclaimed himself emperor.

326
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:11,020
Your Majesty appointed

327
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:11,900
Xia Song and Fan Yong

328
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:14,100
to guard Jingzhou and Yanzhou.

329
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:15,820
With the help of the Imperial Guards,

330
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:18,700
Yuanhao’s troops were repelled from the border

331
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:19,780
and returned empty-handed.

332
00:18:21,540 --> 00:18:24,700
Their morale has been impaired.

333
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:27,340
Your Majesty,

334
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:30,660
I agree to the peace negotiation.

335
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:32,660
But first,

336
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:36,660
we should condemn their overreach

337
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:39,220
and demand that Yuanhao abandon his title

338
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,500
and pay his respects as Your Majesty’s servant.

339
00:18:44,780 --> 00:18:45,860
What do you think, Deputy Censor Yan?

340
00:18:49,380 --> 00:18:50,180
I think

341
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:53,700
it’s too early for the peace negotiation.

342
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:57,140
Huirou,

343
00:18:57,580 --> 00:18:59,260
you’ve been out here for long.

344
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:00,580
Let’s go back.

345
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,820
I want that bird.

346
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:05,900
You can see

347
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:07,300
the bird

348
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,980
but how can you catch it?

349
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:13,820
Huirou,

350
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:17,940
I know you’re the sweetest girl.

351
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:20,420
It’s not because you still want to play outside

352
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,500
that you don’t want to go back, right?

353
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:24,980
No.

354
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,220
Huirou,

355
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:29,580
can you tell me

356
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,900
why you refuse to go back?

357
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:36,700
You know, I prepared

358
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,740
candies and sweet soup

359
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:41,300
for your brother, Miss Gao

360
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:43,340
and you.

361
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:45,580
If you don’t go back,

362
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,060
they can’t eat them either.

363
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:51,100
I know you love birds.

364
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:54,300
I’ll ask the Imperial Artist

365
00:19:54,660 --> 00:19:57,100
to paint

366
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:58,820
a Birds Chirping in the Willow for you,

367
00:19:58,940 --> 00:20:00,100
alright?

368
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:02,220
I don’t want the painting.

369
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,260
I want real birds.

370
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:06,620
Do you want to catch them

371
00:20:06,620 --> 00:20:07,820
so that they can sing to your father?

372
00:20:11,900 --> 00:20:14,420
I have an idea.

373
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:16,660
They can send a message to him.

374
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:20,380
Mr. Yan proposed besiegement

375
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:21,420
to expand the victory.

376
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:24,300
General Li Shibin of Ansai,

377
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:26,140
who’s called Iron Wall by the Qiang

378
00:20:26,140 --> 00:20:27,980
for his victories,

379
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:29,740
has requested to battle repeatedly.

380
00:20:30,740 --> 00:20:32,780
The geographical condition

381
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:34,580
makes it difficult to gather the troops.

382
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:38,540
Massive attacks should be launched cautiously.

383
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:41,500
The northwest is poor.

384
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:44,060
If more troops are dispatched to the west,

385
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:47,980
grains they need have to be delivered first.

386
00:20:48,460 --> 00:20:50,140
Set aside

387
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:52,780
the cost of manpower,

388
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,140
if the army marches forward into the place

389
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:57,420
where the Han and the Qiang cohabitate,

390
00:20:57,700 --> 00:21:00,900
delivering grains can be difficult.

391
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:06,340
The cost of manpower

392
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,300
can’t be ignored.

393
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:17,700
We can’t expand the victory

394
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:19,940
or negotiate for peace.

395
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:22,180
Mr. Yan,

396
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:23,620
do you have a better idea?

397
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:28,940
I’m inexperienced in war

398
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:31,580
and have no better idea.

399
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,380
But I do remember

400
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:37,140
even when Yuanhao’s grandfather Jiqian

401
00:21:37,540 --> 00:21:38,860
was defeated repeatedly,

402
00:21:39,180 --> 00:21:40,660
he still refused to surrender.

403
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:42,660
He was desperate

404
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:45,540
but chose to flee to the desert

405
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:47,380
to stop our troops from chasing him.

406
00:21:47,780 --> 00:21:50,500
Once he was slightly recovered,

407
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:52,180
he raided our border again.

408
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:02,100
Over the past decade, Yuanhao’s father Deming

409
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:03,780
laid a solid foundation for him.

410
00:22:04,060 --> 00:22:05,860
Now, the land and grains he owns

411
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,260
are much more than those of his grandfather Jiqian.

412
00:22:08,860 --> 00:22:09,700
His behavior clearly shows

413
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:12,060
that he’s tougher and more violent.

414
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:13,940
Besides, he already made himself emperor.

415
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:15,740
He wouldn’t want to make peace

416
00:22:16,060 --> 00:22:17,260
after a few narrow defeats.

417
00:22:17,820 --> 00:22:18,740
The Tanguts

418
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:20,460
have been wavering between Song and Liao for years.

419
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:22,900
They are cunning and dishonest.

420
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,060
They can’t be trusted.

421
00:22:28,820 --> 00:22:29,780
Zongshi

422
00:22:29,780 --> 00:22:31,180
has been studying all afternoon.

423
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:32,820
Can he

424
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:34,220
= Zhao Zongshi =
also play with us?

425
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:39,020
Reading and writing are daily routines.

426
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,660
Zongshi is ten times better than you.

427
00:22:41,460 --> 00:22:43,220
You’re allowed to play.

428
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:45,180
Why would I stop him?

429
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:47,460
All his studies have made him a dork.

430
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:49,900
Without your permission,

431
00:22:50,060 --> 00:22:50,980
he won’t join us.

432
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:54,700
You’re smarter

433
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:55,860
because you study less?

434
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:03,900
Brother, brother.

435
00:23:05,380 --> 00:23:07,420
Write a letter to birds.

436
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:10,380
Write it for me.

437
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:12,540
I’m still confused

438
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:15,740
about yesterday’s texts.

439
00:23:19,780 --> 00:23:20,660
Madam Miao,

440
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:25,620
go with Huirou and Taotao

441
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:27,460
to make a kite

442
00:23:27,460 --> 00:23:28,340
to deliver messages to swallows and birds.

443
00:23:31,620 --> 00:23:32,460
Zongshi,

444
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:35,860
let me help you

445
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:37,260
to understand

446
00:23:37,260 --> 00:23:38,980
those texts

447
00:23:39,580 --> 00:23:40,460
that confuse you.

448
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:53,740
Your Majesty,

449
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:54,700
this broth

450
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:55,540
was stewed

451
00:23:55,540 --> 00:23:56,540
with meat stock

452
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:57,460
for 24 hours.

453
00:23:57,740 --> 00:23:58,740
The meat

454
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:01,100
is the tenderloin

455
00:24:01,100 --> 00:24:02,700
of three five-day-old lambs.

456
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:04,740
I found this recipe.

457
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:06,420
Have a taste.

458
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:12,860
To cook this soup

459
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,340
with that meat,

460
00:24:14,980 --> 00:24:16,980
three newborn lambs were killed.

461
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:18,740
You know,

462
00:24:18,740 --> 00:24:19,900
how big they could grow

463
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:21,820
if they lived for two more weeks

464
00:24:22,620 --> 00:24:24,460
and how long they could feed

465
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:25,620
a big family?

466
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:27,660
A sheep

467
00:24:28,060 --> 00:24:29,420
is enough for two shifts of guards in the west

468
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:30,260
to eat.

469
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:37,940
Take it away.

470
00:24:43,140 --> 00:24:44,660
I have no appetite,

471
00:24:44,860 --> 00:24:46,300
and now, I feel worse.

472
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:49,260
Don’t ever serve

473
00:24:49,260 --> 00:24:50,500
such extravagant

474
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:52,660
and costly dishes again.

475
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:04,260
You can leave as well.

476
00:25:10,820 --> 00:25:11,460
What now?

477
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:13,940
You’re also disobeying my order?

478
00:25:18,380 --> 00:25:20,620
Look how disobedient you are!

479
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:22,420
Can’t I criticize you

480
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,420
for your mistake?

481
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,100
If you continue to act like this,

482
00:25:26,300 --> 00:25:27,660
even if you have my protection,

483
00:25:27,780 --> 00:25:28,660
if others see you like this

484
00:25:28,660 --> 00:25:29,500
and report it to censors...

485
00:25:29,500 --> 00:25:31,180
I only care about your feelings.

486
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:33,220
Censors or ministers

487
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:34,540
can call me well-mannered

488
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:35,580
or unruly,

489
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,540
I don’t care.

490
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:38,260
I never want to be a saintess.

491
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,700
Others can pretend to be nice

492
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:41,500
in order to be praised.

493
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,580
I can’t care less.

494
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:46,460
You don’t care?

495
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,020
You know how many complaints

496
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:50,900
I’ve received?

497
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,260
I’m only a maid

498
00:25:55,260 --> 00:25:56,580
looking after your daily routine.

499
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:58,300
I only want you

500
00:25:58,300 --> 00:26:00,020
to eat and sleep properly

501
00:26:00,420 --> 00:26:01,820
and to cheer you up when you’re upset.

502
00:26:02,580 --> 00:26:03,860
Isn’t that my duty?

503
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:05,780
I have no title

504
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:06,780
and I don’t want one.

505
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:08,180
Why did they criticize me?

506
00:26:12,740 --> 00:26:14,820
Seeing you inappetent and sleepless,

507
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:16,100
it pained me.

508
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:18,620
So I cooked a nutritious dish

509
00:26:18,700 --> 00:26:20,060
for your health.

510
00:26:20,060 --> 00:26:21,220
How was that wrong?

511
00:26:22,220 --> 00:26:23,340
Three lambs,

512
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:24,820
soup stewed for 24 hours,

513
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:25,780
they’re nothing!

514
00:26:26,340 --> 00:26:27,700
If blood in my heart

515
00:26:27,860 --> 00:26:28,980
can make you eat more

516
00:26:28,980 --> 00:26:29,820
and become healthier,

517
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:31,540
I’ll drain it without hesitation.

518
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:39,060
I know you care about me,

519
00:26:40,020 --> 00:26:41,300
but I’m no ordinary man.

520
00:26:41,380 --> 00:26:42,420
I’m the Emperor,

521
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:45,100
the ruler of the state.

522
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:46,820
Court officials,

523
00:26:46,820 --> 00:26:48,500
staff in the palace are all watching me.

524
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:52,140
You devote yourself to the state

525
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:54,420
and so do officials, censors

526
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:56,220
and the saintlike Empress.

527
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:57,580
All of them

528
00:26:57,580 --> 00:26:58,740
dedicate themselves to this country,

529
00:26:58,740 --> 00:26:59,740
court and people.

530
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:01,660
They don’t need me.

531
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:03,780
Besides,

532
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,260
those people were never nice to me.

533
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:07,820
After my father passed away,

534
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:08,820
my mother and I

535
00:27:08,860 --> 00:27:10,420
were despised and bullied by them.

536
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:11,660
Those people

537
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:12,940
Aren’t my concern.

538
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:14,340
You’re kind to me,

539
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:16,580
so I only care about you.

540
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:25,860
Fine, alright.

541
00:27:27,580 --> 00:27:28,740
In term of arguing,

542
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:30,500
ten of me combined

543
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:32,460
aren’t your match.

544
00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:40,420
If one day I can make you understand

545
00:27:40,940 --> 00:27:42,580
benevolence, loyalty and other virtues,

546
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:45,060
I’ll be able to teach others

547
00:27:46,260 --> 00:27:47,260
and write my own book.

548
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:54,860
Are you still mad at me?

549
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,100
Anyway,

550
00:27:59,380 --> 00:28:00,380
don’t bring me anything

551
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:02,060
luxurious or costly again.

552
00:28:02,100 --> 00:28:03,460
That won’t make me feel better

553
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,260
but only the opposite.

554
00:28:09,860 --> 00:28:10,940
If you dislike that,

555
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:12,540
I’ll stop doing it.

556
00:28:18,620 --> 00:28:19,420
Let me

557
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:21,740
prepare paper and ink for you

558
00:28:22,020 --> 00:28:24,020
and stay with you when you work.

559
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:27,820
With you here,

560
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:29,340
I’ll only get distracted.

561
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:30,940
How could I work?

562
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:36,380
Go to the kitchen

563
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,860
to cook a bowl of noodles for me.

564
00:28:39,780 --> 00:28:40,620
I’m still hungry.

565
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:44,380
Yes.

566
00:28:54,660 --> 00:28:55,540
That’s too much.

567
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,580
Mr. Hu taught me

568
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:08,100
that poems express

569
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:10,060
happiness, anger, sorrow and joy.

570
00:29:10,660 --> 00:29:11,980
They’re emotions.

571
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:13,900
According to Mr. Hu,

572
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:16,100
Confucius stressed

573
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:17,460
that his disciples should learn poems.

574
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:20,060
Emotions are induced by things outside.

575
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:21,740
They can be written in poems and music.

576
00:29:22,380 --> 00:29:23,380
By following the rhythm

577
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:25,140
when chanting them,

578
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:26,460
you’ll be touched.

579
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,580
When I was still at home,

580
00:29:29,060 --> 00:29:30,300
my teacher said

581
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:34,140
people are kind by nature.

582
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:36,780
If they can keep their nature

583
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:38,740
without being affected by emotions,

584
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:41,180
they can become sages and gentlemen.

585
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:44,820
But most people failed

586
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:47,260
and abandoned their good nature,

587
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:48,620
so they became evil.

588
00:29:49,380 --> 00:29:51,180
Emotions can be destructive,

589
00:29:51,580 --> 00:29:53,420
