630
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:46,460
Different isn’t equal to wrong.

631
00:32:48,060 --> 00:32:49,100
Do you mean

632
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:51,420
although my previous teacher said

633
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:52,860
emotions are bad

634
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:54,860
