636
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:58,260
their sayings are different

637
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,980
yet not wrong.

638
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:02,540
People are born

639
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:03,900
to be good.

640
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:07,940
They own all kinds of virtues.

641
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:13,820
After stimulated by other things,

642
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:16,500
emotions are produced,

643
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:17,620
such as joy and sorrow,

644
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:19,940
love and sadness.

645
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,700
I believe the so-called bad emotions

646
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:26,340
that can destroy people’s good nature

647
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:27,700
are those

648
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:29,620
