650
00:33:33,060 --> 00:33:34,860
which will hurt themselves and others.

651
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:39,220
What Mr. Hu meant

652
00:33:40,180 --> 00:33:41,460
is those from the heart

653
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:44,900
and is within the limit.

654
00:33:45,660 --> 00:33:46,500
Your Highness.

655
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,180
Your Highness.

656
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:52,900
We finished the kite

657
00:33:53,060 --> 00:33:54,780
wrote all our messages for the birds

658
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:55,860
